# API Keys for AI Providers
#
# Add API keys for the providers you want to use.
# The environment variable names are defined in each provider's YAML config.
# See providers/*.yaml for the exact env var names required by each provider.
#
# Examples:
# FAL_KEY="your_fal_api_key_here"
# MESHY_API_KEY="your_meshy_api_key_here"
